Plural forms of all nouns, most verbs, and some adjectives are
provided. Where appropriate, &ldquo;classical&rdquo; variants (for example: &ldquo;brother&rdquo; -&gt;
&ldquo;brethren&rdquo;, &ldquo;dogma&rdquo; -&gt; &ldquo;dogmata&rdquo;, etc.) are also provided.

