Adjectives that are correctly handled include: &ldquo;numerical&rdquo; adjectives
(&ldquo;a&rdquo; -&gt; &ldquo;some&rdquo;), demonstrative adjectives (&ldquo;this&rdquo; -&gt; &ldquo;these&rdquo;, &ldquo;that&rdquo; -&gt;
&ldquo;those&rdquo;), and possessives (&ldquo;my&rdquo; -&gt; &ldquo;our&rdquo;, &ldquo;cat&rsquo;s&rdquo; -&gt; &ldquo;cats&rsquo;&rdquo;, &ldquo;child&rsquo;s&rdquo;
